### Checklist

Before submitting, please ensure:

- [ ] I have analyzed these packages using my own GitHub token
- [ ] I have exported the results using `oss-guard export <ecosystem>`
- [ ] I have validated the contribution using `oss-guard validate-contribution <file>`
- [ ] The contribution file is in `data/contributions/` directory
- [ ] I have reviewed the [Community Contribution Guide](../../docs/COMMUNITY_CONTRIBUTION_GUIDE.md)
- [ ] The contribution contains only public package data (no private/proprietary packages)
- [ ] I understand this contribution will be publicly available
